 Îw=dÎw/dt=h(v,w')-h(v,w)=D.sub.W h(v,w)Îw+W;(4)
where DW h(v,w) is the Jacobian of the w subsystem vector field with respect to w only, that is: an (n-m)Ã(n-m) linear operator (matrix)

